function Start()

	Hydra.Wait(2.5)
	idChief = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(S_CHIEF_FOLLOWER)	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idChief) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_CHIEF_06, idChief)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	idChiefStatic = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Frac_AncientsCall_Chief_Static")[1]
	idChief = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(S_CHIEF_FOLLOWER)	

	local tPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	for i = 1, #tPlayers do
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_SHAM_01, tPlayers[i])
	end

	--Chief move action
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idChief)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idChief, idChiefStatic, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idChief, idChiefStatic)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(idChief, "ANCIENTS_ARRIVED")
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idChief)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idChief)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idChiefStatic)
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(Hydra.ReferenceLevelArea("QST_Frac_AncestralCall_Boss"))
	local idBossSpawner = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Frac_AncestralCall_Boss")[1]
	Hydra.Wait(3)
	Hydra.ActorAddToBossEncounter(Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_GHOST_BOSS, idBossSpawner, false, 0, 0))
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	
	--end boss fight
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(Hydra.ReferenceLevelArea("QST_Frac_AncestralCall_Boss"))
	
	idChiefStatic = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Frac_AncientsCall_Chief_Static")[1]
	idChiefFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(S_CHIEF_FOLLOWER)	
	
	--Chief move action
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idChiefFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idChiefFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idChiefFollower, idChiefStatic, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idChiefFollower, idChiefStatic)
		Hydra.QActorEventSend(idChiefFollower, "ANCIENTS_BOSS")
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idChiefFollower)
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idChiefFollower)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idChiefStatic) then
		Hydra.QActorSheath(idChiefStatic)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idChiefStatic, ANIM_CHIEF_KNEEL)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idChiefStatic)
	end
	
end
